T1  - International banks as leaders or followers of international business: An historical perspective
AU  - Kindleberger, Charles P.
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 7
IS  - 4
SP  - 583
EP  - 595
PY  - 1983
DA  - 1983/12/01/
